snippet.title: Buddy Pass, New Lower Price, and Special Offers | Rainbow Six Extraction
snippet.description:
FRIENDS PLAY FREE*! Invite two friends to play with you for free for up to 14 days!

Pre-order Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Extraction NOW at your favourite retailer! Check each retailer for availability.

*Offer and dates subject to change. Restrictions apply, including availability, technical and content restrictions. Buddy Pass features may differ. Void where prohibited. More info here: https://ubi.li/BuddyPass

Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six Extraction will be available on January 20th, 2022 on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X | S, Xbox One, Stadia and PC.

For more info: 
www.rainbowsixextraction.com
